{"tid":210803,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果傳布局AR眼鏡 外洩資料露玄機","createTime":"2017-04-21T08:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T03:59:58.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5090dbc924cef7e49d44e5280425e625a9745363","tid":210803,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.rti.org.tw/cache/material_139572852260381_400x300.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fcache%2Fmaterial_139572852260381_400x300.JPG&h=8d3a5a40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n時間：2017-04-21 09:49<br />\n新聞引據：中央社<br />\n<br />\n蘋果有無秘密布局擴增實境(AR)眼鏡？外媒引述外洩的健康安全資料推測，蘋果可能正測試眼鏡搭配頭戴式螢幕的擴增實境產品。<br />\n<br />\n科技新聞網站Gizmodo爆料，一位蘋果健康與安全的承包者彙編一份意外突發事件整理報告，卻錯傳給數百位蘋果員工。根據Gizmodo取得相關資料推測，蘋果可能正在秘密布局一些科技新品。<br />\n<br />\nGizmodo引述報告內容報導，一份2月下旬的文件顯示，有位女性測試者在測試樣品後感覺眼睛不太舒服，在研究過程中，她的眼睛看到好幾點雷射閃光，研究小組協助她進行驗光、並保全樣品以便分析。<br />\n<br />\n另一份3月上旬報告顯示，一位蘋果員工在進行工作後感到眼睛不適，可能跟使用方式有關。這位員工注意到產品洋紅色外殼的安全封印有裂開的情形。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述蘋果內部消息人士推測，相關內容或許可能與蘋果正在測試擴增實境產品有關，推測可能是眼鏡搭配頭戴式螢幕的產品。<br />\n<br />\n國外科技網站Appleinsider報導，蘋果研發結合先進硬體和演算法的擴增實境解決方案，可即時將虛擬物體內嵌在真實環境的動態視訊中，也可以即時移動搬動視訊影像中的物體。<br />\n<br />\n彭博(Bloomberg)先前引述不具名知情人士報導，蘋果數百名工程師正在開發擴增實境技術應用，其中也包括iPhone的相機鏡頭團隊，報導也指出，蘋果正在開發具備擴增實境功能的智慧眼鏡。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，蘋果研發擴增實境的團隊網羅各方業界好手，包括曾在臉書(Facebook)開發Oculus Rift裝置或是在微軟(Microsoft)曾研發HoloLens裝置的業界精英。蘋果也持續併購AR硬體、3D遊戲軟體和擴增實境(VR)軟體新創企業。<br />\n<br />\n外媒日前引述瑞銀(UBS)分析師米盧諾維奇(Steven Milunovich)研究報告指出，蘋果在以色列可能有超過1千位的工程師，投入擴增實境相關的技術研發計畫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rti.org.tw/m/news/detail/?recordId=339574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F%3FrecordId%3D339574&d=fc%2FsVbAXSk%2FqMRyYewxCuDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7d8cf80f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rti.org.tw/m/news/detail/?recordId=339574</a>"},{"pid":"fcafa58473e312120140ad9f81c364928e2ebad7","tid":210803,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:49:10.000Z","msg":"Apple算啦<br />\nE+先發展？人地已經有hololens,magic leap"},{"pid":"72f7ba55676babcf283e57136c2972dd2d7e0701","tid":210803,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07460ffea48b9d1a475cc8d3f76f519d00f1e9c1","tid":210803,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfadac81d5a2497a6d324d9951c1a696ece72ae3","tid":210803,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Apple算啦<br />\nE+先發展？人地已經有hololens,magic leap</blockquote><br />\nApple永遠都唔係先驅者，只會重新設計"},{"pid":"6416befd3dab6bf508d4db0a16914eb90c92473b","tid":210803,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c262fda7a4492142a74fcf93244deda7df0eeb54","tid":210803,"uid":32013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:30:05.000Z","msg":"Google Glass真係先驅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜多年來都量產唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1db7b036e03cbdf312bb1729db4e4f8d6a68c28","tid":210803,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Apple算啦<br />\nE+先發展？人地已經有hololens,magic leap</blockquote><br />\nApple永遠都唔係先驅者，只會重新設計</blockquote><br />\n咪係 apple呢啲叫創新 發揚光大<br />\nan機果啲先係抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bd7b9889ffc18336